        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>Some 91/92/9400 Pro Sleeper models have experienced cracking of the fender extensions due to the
                    weight of snow and ice. To prevent this from occurring, a fender extension reinforcement should be
                    installed on the underside of each rear fender extension splash panel.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
